text: Luchtenburg is a hamlet in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is a part of the municipality of Buren, and is located in about 8 km southwest of Veenendaal.ANWB Topografische Atlas Nederland, Topografische Dienst and ANWB, 2005. ==References== Category:Populated places in Gelderland Category:Buren
title: Luchtenburg
